context menu(mouse right click)
ctrl + enter
and single key stroke to run a command

ctrl shift alt d: select all occurences

ctrl alt -: go back
ctrl alt +: go forward

alt b: test
alt n: run previouse test
alt m: run all test

ctrl shift i: reinident

ls -la: show files including hidden files

ctrl ; go to end of line

ctrl window right-arrow move editor to next group
ctrl window left-arrow move editor to previous group

ctrl j join editors

